            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"主题\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#主题\">#</a> 主题</h1>\n<h2 id=\"创建主题\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#创建主题\">#</a> 创建主题</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bin/kafka-topics.sh --zookeeper localhost:2181/kafka --create --topic topic-demo --partitions 4 --replication-factor 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"查看主题\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#查看主题\">#</a> 查看主题</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bin/kafka-topics.sh --zookeeper localhost:2181/kafka --describe --topic topic-demo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n",
